98650,"uid":81256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:05:11.000Z","msg":"網上睇晒 這書能讓你戒煙<br />\n一般啦 都係果啲大道理"},{"pid":"1f8ec56f9121a73f5dfb48a6566e4cc4adf0ebde","tid":2298650,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f21a622ae19048208a346cec7a6f8e1e49de4c","tid":2298650,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a9cba6397afa584e24940df6f12a5930f058d1","tid":2298650,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d68a82be8f41bf534e2eaa0bae7d30ef80793e","tid":2298650,"uid":99299,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"Ching現家啲煙仔都好貴下喎<br />\n雖然我未試過食煙 但我都明白上癮既感覺 因為之前都打機成癮<br />\n係心情唔好既時候就會去打機<br />\n之後去改變呢個習慣都要好長時間<br />\n我見到樓主你話呢段時間好容易扯火<br />\n可能你之前習慣左係你心情唔好既時侯就去食煙<br />\n所以你係戒煙既時候就容易唔開心<br />\n其實你可以試下搵其他方法去代替 <br />\n例如做下自已中意做既野，做下運動咁<br />\n但我最後都成功捱到 所以我覺得你都得架<br />\n希望你今次都可以成功戒到煙啦"},{"pid":"1c14edd78bd47111e411baab029645d60ed6b74d","tid":2298650,"uid":66198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96b27db014708bdb2a18b69996f808cad1972df7","tid":2298650,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T07:56:16.000Z","msg":"10幾年煙齡<br />\n戒過幾次都失敗<br />\n<br />\n今次算係最有決心<br />\n<br />\n今日Day 6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\